SUMMARY:Stroum Lectures 2026 with Rafael Neis: Did &#8216\;Men&#8217\; a
 nd &#8216\;Women&#8217\; Always Exist? What the Talmud Can Tell Us
LOCATION:Kane Hall (KNE)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260512T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260512T210000
